        protected IMotionExecutionService getControllerExecutionService(com.kuka.resource.IResource device)
        Gets an execution service for the specified device.

        If execution service for the controller of the specified device was not found, new instance will be created.

        Parameters:
        device - device resource for which to get an execution service
        Returns:
        execution service for the specified device, or null if execution service was not found or could not be created
